---
import SiteLayout from '../../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout title="About ReviewPrompt" description="Product positioning and repository purpose." locale="en">
  <section class="aw-page-hero">
    <div class="aw-container">
      <p class="aw-eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>About ReviewPrompt</h1>
      <p>ReviewPrompt is currently focused as an open prompt library for AI-assisted paper review.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="aw-container aw-section compact">
    <div class="aw-content-card">
      <p>The website is designed around two users for now: authors and reviewers.</p>
      <p>It starts with two high-frequency prompts: full paper review and rebuttal response.</p>
      <p>More domains and more tasks can be added after the prompt experience is clear.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
